1. In a Test Suite press "Add wth tag" button;
2. Type tag1 and tag2;
3. Press OK button;
4. Make sure that the test TC_tag1_tag2 is added;
5. In a Test Suite press "Add wth tag" button;
6. Type tag2 & tag3;
7. Press OK button;
8. Make sure that the test TC_tag2_tag3 is added;
